---
// Empty-state for the "upcoming events" list, used on the home page
// and the /events page so the copy and styling stay in sync.
---

<div class="flex items-start gap-4 rounded-2xl border border-amber-200 bg-white/60 p-6">
  <svg
    class="w-8 h-8 text-amber-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5"
    fill="none"
    stroke="currentColor"
    stroke-width="2"
    stroke-linecap="round"
    stroke-linejoin="round"
    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
    aria-hidden="true"
  >
    <path d="M8 2v4" />
    <path d="M16 2v4" />
    <rect width="18" height="18" x="3" y="4" rx="2" />
    <path d="M3 10h18" />
  </svg>
  <p class="text-lg text-stone-600 font-medium">
    <span class="font-bold text-amber-700">No upcoming events scheduled</span>
    &mdash; check back soon for classes, open workshop hours, and community events.
  </p>
</div>
